posts.subject: Welcome!
posts.body:
Salaam Aleikum!

While we wait for 8chan's return, I will try to direct as many of our users as possible to this place. Hopefully we can return to our discussions.

posts.subject: Ahh good
posts.body: I's good to see that some things never truly die. It sucks that /pol/ ruined it for all of us, but stay comfy /v/!

>>1e190170-07e1-4b73-8036-3c8d36aa9e65
>They can't arrest us all.
Oh ... yes, they can.

FREE SPEECH!
FREE SPEECH!
FREE SPEECH!!!!!!!

... oh, but not for you.

posts.subject: Sigh
posts.body: Well, I don't know how many of the /christian/ base will make it here, but we had started working on a novena schedule. Looks like we're going to have to start again unless 8ch returns without anything being deleted.
